    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i just need help with the math. my sensitivity factor is usually around 1:50 (meaning 1 unit drops me about 50 points). if i'm at 185 and want to hit 100, how many units should i bolus right now? just do the quick math for me so i can get back to it.",
